org.jtimer.Regression

Class Regression

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jtimer.Regression.Regression
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Regression>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FlexibleFunctionalFit, FunctionalFit, PolynomialFit

    public abstract class Regression
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Regression>
    An abstract class that acts as a base-line for the other forms of regression. Has methods to compare regressions, calculate the error, and setting the names and an abstract method for calculating f(x).
    Author:
    MagneticZero
